list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Remove appsettings.json files from multiple projects
These appsettings.json files containing sensitive information such as database connection strings were removed from three projects: DataAccessLayer, Project-2, and ProjectAPI. It's part of an effort to increase security and enforce the use of environment variables for sensitive data.

changelist.name: Changes
changelist.comment:
Update workspace.xml and enable documentation generation
Updated workspace.xml with new tasks and improved configurations. Also added code to generate documentation in Project-2.csproj and enhanced swagger setup in Program.cs.

task.summary:
Remove initial DataAccessLayer migrations
The initial migration files for the DataAccessLayer have been removed. This includes the primary migration scripts and associated designer files. The changes are part of a broader project restructure and cleanup, ensuring only necessary files are kept in the repository.

Remove appsettings.json files from multiple projects
These appsettings.json files containing sensitive information such as database connection strings were removed from three projects: DataAccessLayer, Project-2, and ProjectAPI. It's part of an effort to increase security and enforce the use of environment variables for sensitive data.
